<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥnạnk yạ rb ạlạ̉kwạn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ḥnạnk yạ rb ạlạ̉kwạn .. ạ̹lyk rfʿt ṣlạty
 ạ̉nạ ạ̹n ạ̉ḥyạ fbạlạ̹ymạn .. ysẖrf mʿny̱ ḥyạty
 1- smʿt ndạʾk yạ rby .. yjljl fy ạ̉ʿmạqy
 ṣdaⁿy̱ ytjạwb fy qlby .. mʿ ạlngẖm ạlkẖfạq
 fsrt bhdyk fy drby .. wby ẓmạ̉ ạlmsẖtạq
 lmnhlk ạlṣạfy ạlʿdẖb .. ạ̉rwy bh ạ̉mnyạty
 2- yrwʿny ṣkẖb ạlbḥr .. wṣwt qṣyf ạlrʿwd
 fậns mnk mʿ ạlfjr .. bfyḍ ạlrḍạ wạljwd
 fyạ mbdʿ ạlkwn mn ydry .. swạk bsr ạlwjwd
 fkm fyk yạ rb mn sriⁿ .. wậyạtiⁿ mdẖhlạt
 3- ạ̹lhy ạ̹n ạ̉dʿw fmạly .. swạk mjyb ndạỷy
 wḥyn ạ̉nwʾ bạ̉tẖqạly .. fly brḍạk ʿzạỷy
 ṭrḥt mnạyạ wậmạly .. ldyk wkl rjạỷy
 fạ̉nt mlạdẖy wmậly .. ạ̹lyk wfyk njạty</lyrics>
